Mumu said she had a gift for me.

285
00:19:01,360 --> 00:19:03,360
-They are so sweet.
-Mumu, where's the gift?

286
00:19:07,320 --> 00:19:08,880
-Look.
-This is for you.

287
00:19:09,280 --> 00:19:11,520
-Is that a phone case?
-It is.

288
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,320
-Couples cases.
-Matching.

289
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:15,200
-It's a pair.
-Yes.

290
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:17,720
-That's so sweet.
-Absolutely.

291
00:19:18,120 --> 00:19:19,560
-"Muzhou"?
-Look.

292
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:21,320
My gosh!

293
00:19:22,520 --> 00:19:23,840
-Too sweet.
-That's so cute!

294
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:27,720
If you all don't mind,
I'm going to take Mumu with me.

295
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:31,000
-Let's go.
-Yizhou.

296
00:19:32,160 --> 00:19:33,880
-How about a drink first?
-Sure.

297
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:35,800
He can't drink. He has to drive.

298
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:37,840
I can have my driver drive him.

299
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,680
<i>He was injured. He shouldn't be drinking.</i>

300
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:41,720
I'll drink for him.

301
00:19:44,840 --> 00:19:45,760
This is delicious.

302
00:19:48,840 --> 00:19:49,720
Right?

303
00:19:50,120 --> 00:19:51,120
Are you all right?

304
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:53,640
-I'm fine.
-I envy them.

305
00:19:58,720 --> 00:20:00,760
-All right.
-Let's all raise our glasses.

306
00:20:00,840 --> 00:20:01,720
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

307
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:03,040
-Drink up!
-Cheers!

308
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:04,040
Bottoms up!

309
00:20:06,120 --> 00:20:07,600
-It's finally a wrap.
-Yes.

310
00:20:07,680 --> 00:20:08,960
-We're finally done filming.
-Right.

311
00:20:16,320 --> 00:20:17,280
<i>Be careful.</i>

312
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:20,640
-I'm not drunk.
-I know.

313
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:23,920
-I'm good at drinking. Let go.
-I know you are.

314
00:20:24,880 --> 00:20:25,800
Careful.

315
00:20:26,040 --> 00:20:27,800
I'm not drunk.

316
00:20:28,040 --> 00:20:29,040
Let's sit over there.

317
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:31,480
-Let go of me.
-Sit down.

318
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:32,560
Let go...

319
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:01,440
Mumu?

320
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:05,080
Move in with me.

321
00:21:10,040 --> 00:21:11,240
Why should I

322
00:21:12,120 --> 00:21:14,240
move in with you?

323
00:21:16,280 --> 00:21:17,800
I want to protect you at all times.

324
00:21:18,720 --> 00:21:20,320
Protect me?

325
00:21:34,040 --> 00:21:35,560
Mr. Ling?

326
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:37,640
Are you...

327
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:41,640
going to kiss me?

328
00:21:43,720 --> 00:21:46,080
We have an engagement contract.

329
00:21:46,280 --> 00:21:48,800
You can't break the terms.

330
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:50,960
And Jia Fei

331
00:21:51,640 --> 00:21:54,760
got pregnant with Wen Li's baby.

332
00:21:56,040 --> 00:21:57,480
I mean, almost.

333
00:21:59,840 --> 00:22:00,880
So,

334
00:22:01,560 --> 00:22:04,600
